---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="What Should I Eat Today? - Random Food Picker Wheel" description="Spin the food wheel and let fate choose your meal! Add custom options and get a fun food suggestion.">
  <section class="mb-8">
    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="pageDesc">Can not decide <strong>what to eat today</strong>? Spin the <strong>food picker wheel</strong> and let fate choose! Add your own options or use our preset list.</p>
  </section>
  <section id="calculator" class="text-center">
    <div class="mb-6">
      <canvas id="wheelCanvas" width="350" height="350" class="mx-auto rounded-full shadow-lg border-4 border-orange-300"></canvas>
      <div class="text-4xl -mt-2">&#9660;</div>
    </div>
    <button id="spinBtn" class="bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-full text-lg mb-6 transition-all transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg" data-i18n="spinBtn">Spin the Wheel!</button>
    <div id="resultArea" class="hidden mb-6">
      <div class="bg-orange-50 rounded-xl p-6 border-2 border-orange-300">
        <p class="text-sm text-orange-600 mb-1" data-i18n="todayEat">Today you should eat...</p>
        <p id="resultFood" class="text-4xl font-bold text-orange-700 mb-2"></p>
        <p id="resultTagline" class="text-lg text-gray-600 italic"></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 border border-gray-200 text-left mb-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 mb-3" data-i18n="customize">Customize Options (one per line)</p>
      <textarea id="optionsInput" rows="6" class="w-full px-3 py-2 text-sm rounded-lg border border-gray-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-orange-500 focus:outline-none">Hamburger
Pizza
Sushi
Ramen
Salad
Pasta
Tacos
Curry
Stir Fry
BBQ</textarea>
      <button id="updateBtn" class="mt-3 bg-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-700 text-white text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-lg" data-i18n="updateBtn">Update Wheel</button>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="mt-10 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4" data-i18n="whyTitle">Why Use a Random Food Picker?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4" data-i18n="whyDesc">Decision fatigue is real. A <strong>random food wheel</strong> removes the burden of choice and adds fun to meal planning.</p>
  </section>
  <section id="faq" class="mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6" data-i18n="faq">FAQ</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 open:bg-white open:shadow-sm"><summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-sm" data-i18n="fq1">How does the food wheel work?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><p data-i18n="fa1">Click spin and the wheel rotates randomly to land on a food item.</p></div></details>
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 open:bg-white open:shadow-sm"><summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-sm" data-i18n="fq2">Can I add my own foods?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><p data-i18n="fa2">Yes! Edit the text area with one food per line and click Update.</p></div></details>
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 open:bg-white open:shadow-sm"><summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-sm" data-i18n="fq3">Is the spin random?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><p data-i18n="fa3">Yes. Uses Math.random() for rotation angle.</p></div></details>
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 open:bg-white open:shadow-sm"><summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-sm" data-i18n="fq4">How many options?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><p data-i18n="fa4">As many as you want. 6-12 works best for readability.</p></div></details>
      <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 open:bg-white open:shadow-sm"><summary class="cursor-pointer px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-sm" data-i18n="fq5">Mobile friendly?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-gray-600"><p data-i18n="fa5">Yes! Fully responsive on all devices.</p></div></details>
    </div>
  </section>
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How does the food wheel work?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Click spin and the wheel rotates randomly."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I add my own foods?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! One food per line."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is the spin random?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Uses Math.random()."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How many options?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"6-12 works best."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Mobile friendly?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes! Fully responsive."}}]}</script>
